== 發行 ==

=== 評價 ===
《神通鬼大》得到了影評人普遍積極的評價。截至2014年6月，透過影評網站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]收集的36篇評論中，有64%給予好評，[[加權平均數|平均分為]]6.2/10；該網站共識：「擁有頂尖的特效及彼得·傑克森驚人的導演能力，《神通鬼大》在視覺上十分醒目，但不協調。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/frighteners/|title=The Frighteners|work=Rotten Tomatoes|publisher=Flixster|accessdate=2014-06-08|archive-date=2014-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140912205202/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/frighteners/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

評論家{{link-en|克里斯托弗·努爾|Christopher Null}}稱讚了這部電影，描述其為「《[[魔鬼剋星|魔鬼剋星]]》與《[[雙峰_(電視劇)|雙峰]]》的混合體」<ref name="null">{{cite news|url=http://www.filmcritic.com/misc/emporium.nsf/reviews/The-Frighteners |author=Null, Christopher |year=1996 |publisher={{link-en|Filmcritic.com|Filmcritic.com}} |title=The Frighteners |accessdate=2009-02-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080709064126/http://www.filmcritic.com/misc/emporium.nsf/reviews/The-Frighteners |archivedate=2008-07-09 }}</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]的邁克爾·德魯克表示，雖然《神通鬼大》不會是傑克遜電影中的前五名，但形容它為「一個無害而有趣的黑色喜劇，令你百看不厭」<ref name=Kong>{{cite news | author = Drucker, Michael | title = I Can't Believe It's Not Burton | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | url = http://dvd.ign.com/articles/675/675620p1.html | date = 2005-12-14 | accessdate = 2008-12-24 | archive-date = 2012-02-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120224120802/http://dvd.ign.com/articles/675/675620p1.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。電影同時受到了紐西蘭影評人褒貶不一的評價<ref name=fright>Pryor, p.206-211</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
電影於美國的1,675個劇院發行，並在首映週末位居第五位，共收穫5,565,495美元，平均每場劇院3,335美元。最終全球累計29,359,216美元<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=frighteners.htm | title = The Frighteners | work = [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] | accessdate = 2008-12-24 | archive-date = 2016-02-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160209035906/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=frighteners.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《神通鬼大》之所以會成為[[票房炸彈|票房炸彈]]，主要原因為《[[ID4星際終結者|ID4星際終結者]]》的競爭<ref>{{cite news | author = Woods, Mark | title = "Daylight" in Money O'Seas | url = http://www.variety.com/vstory/VR1117436171 | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = 1996-12-31| accessdate = 2008-12-24}}</ref>。

